{"tid":1886811,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打試過隻火牛無撚啦啦著返","createTime":"2020-02-19T07:03:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T02:36:27.000Z","uid":67976,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"26aafd2239fb4e5d2885be969926a0c3b6c03ba9","tid":1886811,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:03:16.000Z","msg":"本身部電腦掛緊機<br />\n<br />\n琴日朝早起身睇無啦啦熄左 火牛盞燈唔著 用埋萬字夾short線都無反應<br />\n開機同無插電源一樣咩反應都無 心諗應該係隻牛打柴<br />\n<br />\n我凌晨再試一次都係咁 咁就諗住今日去買過隻牛<br />\n<br />\n買完隻牛點知一返到屋企再鳩試下啪返隻火牛<br />\n著燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁隊返落塊坂度試下 又真係順利開到機<br />\n咁我新買隻牛就企左喺度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無巴打隻牛都係新界牛黎？"},{"pid":"6376419ff5b23f5935bb8a04077dd0d28aebc393","tid":1886811,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:06:28.000Z","msg":"本身係直插定插拖板？"},{"pid":"0eb3a118fe69ca4629e11ce2d9f76cc8442903cc","tid":1886811,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6376419ff5b23f5935bb8a04077dd0d28aebc393","tid":1886811,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:06:28.000Z","msg":"本身係直插定插拖板？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:13:32.000Z","msg":"插拖板 但我拎埋其它電器試埋同一個位 都係著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家都係插同一個位"},{"pid":"9cea6112a1f083a54f63a2d72a303ec6dad20f37","tid":1886811,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0eb3a118fe69ca4629e11ce2d9f76cc8442903cc","tid":1886811,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6376419ff5b23f5935bb8a04077dd0d28aebc393","tid":1886811,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:06:28.000Z","msg":"本身係直插定插拖板？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:13:32.000Z","msg":"插拖板 但我拎埋其它電器試埋同一個位 都係著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家都係插同一個位"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:18:11.000Z","msg":"反正買咗新 都換咗佢啦<br />\n<br />\n一陣佢真係放煙花"},{"pid":"a111850f7fc3869713626e1eeb75d866008152fd","tid":1886811,"uid":69994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T07:26:43.000Z","msg":"PPTC（Polymeric Positive Temperature Coefficient），即高分子聚合物正係數溫度元件。又稱可復式保險絲（Resettable Fuse）或聚合物保險絲（Polyfuse），在中國大陸的電子業界俗稱自恢復保險絲或過流保護片。<br />\n特性與應用<br />\nPPTC特性是在正常電流情況下呈現低電阻，約數m&Omega;到數&Omega;之間。<span style=\"color: red;\">在過電流故障下，電阻急劇升高，從而保護後端電路。由於具有優異的可恢復特性，用於過電流保護時，在故障消除之後，電路可自動恢復到導通狀態。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Resettable_fuse\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FResettable_fuse&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDns01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=b63b6ddd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Resettable_fuse</a>"},{"pid":"455bc898dabc61d450c7fdbc940197152ff1a762","tid":1886811,"uid":38891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T13:15:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sd23qmi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsd23qmi.jpg&h=3f6324cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我當初就係照用新界牛....."},{"pid":"63a3675dcf97f6b51b1e6cbd73adc0acda8ee995","tid":1886811,"uid":37107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"455bc898dabc61d450c7fdbc940197152ff1a762","tid":1886811,"uid":38891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T13:15:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sd23qmi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsd23qmi.jpg&h=3f6324cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我當初就係照用新界牛....."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T02:36:27.000Z","msg":"痴線係地府都上到連登"}]}